highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Lo Siento BB:/ (with Bad Bunny & Julieta Venegas)” is the highest at #25.
“I’m Tired (with Zendaya) - Bonus Track” by Labrinth and Zendaya is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #82.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 265 weeks straight.
“Yo Voy (feat. Daddy Yankee)” by Zion & Lennox is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 83 spots at #100.
